Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別離之鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去…是去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要親手把你埋葬掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老爹大人在我身上施下了秘術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  本大爺的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向城堡進發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去支援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻  到底要帶我去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來就會知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想跟小狼他們以及鎮上的人們去領主的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說幾遍你才能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在還有其它必須要去做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一種像已經去世了的媽媽的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佔領這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡裡的秘術已經消失了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡看守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘的人們  跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  你的力量就只有這種程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我老爹的秘術是無敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不僅移動的速度很快  而且還會變形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  一會噗嚕嚕的膨脹  一會又縮小了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小傢伙們還有些能耐的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠撐到現在的人類  除了你們這些小傢伙外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有過去曾跟我交手的蓮姬女秘術師了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該是春香的母親了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像說過她有個叫這個名字的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座城鎮真正需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個愚蠢的領主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是你們這些小傢伙和那個女秘術師這樣的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是現在的我無法離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也不得不聽從那個任意操縱我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽從他那不知分寸的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然惋惜你們這些小傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但差不多也該結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  這就叫做「最大的危機」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是被吞噬還是腐蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一種都鐵定是沒命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這可真傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在可還不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況下卻還不使用魔法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我無關啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  黑咪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還要回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到原來的世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白饅頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找到那位公主的羽毛之前應該不會移動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就儘快解決掉儘快到下一個世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不怎麼想在同一個地方待太久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長眠在我原本所在國家的水底的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我就會被他追上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不得不逃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到各式各樣的世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺言都說完了是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種大難臨頭的感覺了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急著想死嗎  小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼  小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用秘術變出來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說政府的暗行御使也是個秘術高手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是暗行御使嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的話我更應該在這裡解決你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻腳是被秘妖傷到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？痛吧  不好受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是擅長使用踢技的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過於在意傷腳的話可是贏不了本大爺的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會受影響的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是哪裡受傷都不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定要做的事情  就要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當不錯的計策嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點讓雨停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個秘妖居然會被打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能會輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為蓮姬領主的…老爹大人秘術的力…力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…無敵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼獲勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙可以利用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再敢輕舉妄動的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  這次是施了什麼秘術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為封在那顆石頭裡的秘術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才會被領主囚禁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個被黑碰給破壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那對愚蠢的領主父子相比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想阻擋有骨氣的小傢伙們前進呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要使出卑鄙的手段了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是領主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗我的秘術的恐怖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮由於領主的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個都改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣走出城鎮外面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感覺到難以忘懷的風景依然存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該是第一次來這個城鎮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母…母親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想見你  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:14:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再讓那些小鬼們胡作非為下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白這是什麼意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時聽令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼媽媽的靈魂能附著在小櫻的身上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為  領主把我的靈魂封閉在門內了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我作對的人  都不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽的靈魂將無法升天入地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能永遠飄蕩在荒蕪的異世界之間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻攔我的人都除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮是我的了  哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封在門內的我  仍然有著特別的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等待神所眷顧的女孩的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後終於等到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有著神的祝福的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請勇敢地去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和所愛的人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回那應該回去的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是母親給我展示對大樹施展秘術的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然沒有憑藉任何秘術的道具…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道具只是用來增加秘術的力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的力量展現給媽媽看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我發揮不出來像母親那樣的力量呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為  你把我說過的話給忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候  我說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親…說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘術是一種能給人帶來幸福的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能為了一己私利而去使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  我總是抱著用秘術來打倒領主的愚蠢想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那樣是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓別人獲得幸福而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成…成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  伸過手來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘術之鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘術之鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去給人帶來幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多也該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  這次真的要分別了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  母親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想和您待在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠留在我身邊好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  總有一天  我會用秘術讓媽媽復活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是實現不了的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是擁有多麼強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逝去的生命  也再也回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此  生命才顯出它的可貴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽會一直在你身邊注視著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去城堡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  原來是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嚇唬我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵從領主大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要帶你們走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎？摩可拿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這裡的不可思議的力量最強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於  到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:20:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小櫻的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  是在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能破解我的秘術
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你們是政府的暗行御使嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放她們下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向政府稟報了我的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就算是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連暗行御使都可以打倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放她們兩個下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢再碰我一下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人就沒命了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個鎮上的鎮民
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.58,0:22:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢攻打我的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對他們施了秘術
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了我隨心所欲操縱的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想對這些人動手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.26,0:24:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼與邪惡的領主的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.25,0:24:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於進入了高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.59,0:24:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小櫻和春香被作為人質
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.50,0:24:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼出現大危機
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.07,0:24:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這時出現了意料之外的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.44,0:24:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫了一個大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？暗行御使們好像從什麼地方看到過？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.45,0:24:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長的是什麼樣子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.01,0:24:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就請繼續期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.93,0:24:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼·年代記
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.98,0:24:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十一話  被選擇的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.73,0:24:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的藍色紋章會讓人期待不已


